== List of countries entirely south of the Tropic of Capricorn ==
As most of Earth&#x27;s land is in the Northern Hemisphere only four countries are wholly south of the Tropic of Capricorn (which contrasts with 73, about one third of the current total, wholly north of the Tropic of Cancer):
* Eswatini (formerly Swaziland)
* Lesotho
* New Zealand
* Uruguay

